WEBVTT


00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:22.940
♪Only after bloom comes fruit♪

00:00:24.350 --> 00:00:28.320
♪Who says glory must fade to the past♪

00:00:30.980 --> 00:00:36.070
♪Only through thunder
do you reach the clouds♪

00:00:37.270 --> 00:00:42.180
♪Who made you the crown of every peak♪

00:00:43.710 --> 00:00:46.990
♪I stand at the center of the stage♪

00:00:46.990 --> 00:00:50.060
♪My shadow is pinned against the wall♪

00:00:50.770 --> 00:00:55.720
♪Facing the light earns every medal♪

00:00:56.760 --> 00:00:59.940
♪Little birds,
save your needless pecking♪

00:00:59.940 --> 00:01:03.220
♪The open sky rises high♪

00:01:03.760 --> 00:01:08.890
♪When night falls,
the moon begins to shine♪

00:01:09.660 --> 00:01:12.920
♪I stand in the heart of these lands♪

00:01:12.920 --> 00:01:16.280
♪My shadow bears no crown or robe♪

00:01:16.690 --> 00:01:22.360
♪Then I know truth needs no disguise♪

00:01:22.770 --> 00:01:26.020
♪The green hills see me as I am♪

00:01:26.020 --> 00:01:29.350
♪Like dew, lightning,
and moon on the river♪

00:01:29.750 --> 00:01:33.790
♪Showing me exactly who I am♪

00:01:33.790 --> 00:01:35.040
=The Lead=

00:01:36.020 --> 00:01:37.940
=Episode 34=

00:01:38.760 --> 00:01:39.600
What is it?

00:01:40.080 --> 00:01:41.040
What's the matter?

00:01:41.400 --> 00:01:42.320
Sit.

00:01:42.400 --> 00:01:43.560
Sit, and I'll tell you.

00:01:45.720 --> 00:01:46.880
The troupe's lead drummer

00:01:47.960 --> 00:01:48.800
broke a bone.

00:01:49.520 --> 00:01:50.720
He really broke a bone?

00:01:51.720 --> 00:01:52.880
What, you knew about this?

00:01:52.960 --> 00:01:53.920
No, I didn't.

00:01:55.320 --> 00:01:57.240
The premiere is tomorrow.

00:01:57.600 --> 00:01:59.360
You gotta come save the day.

00:02:01.760 --> 00:02:02.600
Me?

00:02:06.160 --> 00:02:08.320
What about the other lead drummers?

00:02:08.360 --> 00:02:10.400
Isn't it against the rules to ask me?

00:02:10.600 --> 00:02:11.800
Forget about the rules.

00:02:11.800 --> 00:02:12.760
The other lead drummers

00:02:12.760 --> 00:02:13.760
are way too young.

00:02:13.760 --> 00:02:14.880
They lack that energy.

00:02:14.880 --> 00:02:16.080
Come give us that energy.

00:02:16.560 --> 00:02:17.560
Besides,

00:02:17.560 --> 00:02:20.720
it's Qin'e's debut in Chang'an.

00:02:21.640 --> 00:02:23.320
Would you trust anyone else with it?

00:02:23.640 --> 00:02:25.160
Do you trust me with it?

00:02:25.160 --> 00:02:26.920
Of course, I do.

00:02:27.120 --> 00:02:29.280
You must play the Zhangu drum anyway.

00:02:29.280 --> 00:02:31.240
You need to set the tone for us.

00:02:31.310 --> 00:02:32.180
Right?

00:02:32.200 --> 00:02:33.440
Here, take the score.

00:02:34.040 --> 00:02:35.600
(You Xi Hu score)
Learn it quickly.

00:02:36.080 --> 00:02:38.280
Rehearsal is this afternoon.

00:02:38.920 --> 00:02:40.880
By the way, what did you need today?

00:02:42.920 --> 00:02:43.760
Nothing.

00:02:43.920 --> 00:02:44.760
I...

00:02:45.080 --> 00:02:46.920
was just passing by to see you.

00:02:49.680 --> 00:02:50.520
San Yuan,

00:02:51.040 --> 00:02:52.920
ruining a show is a deadly mistake.

00:02:53.520 --> 00:02:55.440
Now my fate and the fate of this show

00:02:56.240 --> 00:02:57.760
are both in your hands.

00:02:58.240 --> 00:02:59.080
Alright.

00:03:29.120 --> 00:03:30.560
Why aren't we there yet?

00:03:31.080 --> 00:03:32.160
How long was I asleep?

00:03:33.080 --> 00:03:34.160
Who knows?

00:03:40.040 --> 00:03:41.160
Where are you taking me?

00:03:43.840 --> 00:03:44.800
Where are we?

00:03:45.240 --> 00:03:46.160
No idea.

00:03:46.840 --> 00:03:48.880
I was looking, but the road just ended.

00:03:49.880 --> 00:03:50.720
Stop the car.

00:03:52.080 --> 00:03:53.600
I can't stop here. Just wait a sec.

00:03:53.600 --> 00:03:55.600
I said stop the car! Did you hear me?

00:03:55.600 --> 00:03:57.240
It's uphill. I can't stop now.

00:03:57.240 --> 00:03:58.160
Stop the car!

00:03:58.160 --> 00:03:59.880
Okay, okay, stop grabbing me.

00:03:59.880 --> 00:04:00.720
- Stop!
- I'll stop

00:04:00.720 --> 00:04:01.640
when I get to the top.

00:04:01.640 --> 00:04:02.880
- To the top.
- Stop now!

00:04:02.880 --> 00:04:04.080
Okay, I'm stopping!

00:04:07.880 --> 00:04:08.880
Why did you bring me here?

00:04:10.240 --> 00:04:12.160
I worried you'd be nervous on stage.

00:04:12.160 --> 00:04:13.240
So I took you out to relax.

00:04:14.160 --> 00:04:15.720
I heard about the Eight Views of Chang'an.

00:04:16.760 --> 00:04:18.440
Thought a hike would help you relax.

00:04:19.320 --> 00:04:21.520
Who knew we'd run out of road?

00:04:21.840 --> 00:04:22.840
I've been here

00:04:22.840 --> 00:04:23.960
with my buddies before.

00:04:23.960 --> 00:04:25.640
But as I kept driving...

00:04:25.680 --> 00:04:26.800
After that intersection,

00:04:26.800 --> 00:04:28.440
the road just disappeared.

00:04:34.000 --> 00:04:35.200
Where are you going?

00:04:44.120 --> 00:04:45.960
Stop driving, it's a dead end.

00:04:50.840 --> 00:04:52.040
The view here is beautiful.

00:04:53.000 --> 00:04:53.880
Let's stay here.

00:04:54.840 --> 00:04:55.680
Thirsty?

00:04:55.960 --> 00:04:56.880
Have a soda.

00:04:58.400 --> 00:05:00.080
We came prepared.

00:05:02.880 --> 00:05:03.800
If you ask me,

00:05:04.160 --> 00:05:06.360
people in Chang'an haven't seen much.

00:05:06.800 --> 00:05:07.680
Evening Glow over

00:05:07.680 --> 00:05:09.880
Mount Li, compared to
Ningzhou's Sixty-Six Bends,

00:05:10.120 --> 00:05:11.000
is not even close.

00:05:13.040 --> 00:05:14.200
Ningzhou is over there.

00:05:18.560 --> 00:05:19.400
Do you miss home?

00:05:22.560 --> 00:05:23.800
I left home at twelve

00:05:24.720 --> 00:05:26.640
and haven't really been back since.

00:05:33.400 --> 00:05:34.240
I don't miss it.

00:05:35.200 --> 00:05:36.320
Who asked you?

00:05:38.680 --> 00:05:39.680
I just don't.

00:05:40.960 --> 00:05:42.320
Back when I was in Beishan,

00:05:42.800 --> 00:05:45.240
everyone thought I rode
on my dad's coattails.

00:05:45.760 --> 00:05:46.960
I just don't like that place.

00:05:48.200 --> 00:05:49.400
Well, did you?

00:05:50.400 --> 00:05:51.320
I didn't want to.

00:05:52.120 --> 00:05:53.120
But I had no choice.

00:05:53.400 --> 00:05:54.640
Everyone knows I'm his son.

00:05:54.640 --> 00:05:56.360
Everything I do represents him.

00:05:56.880 --> 00:05:58.880
He never asks what I want to do.

00:06:02.800 --> 00:06:04.200
Now that I'm in Chang'an,

00:06:04.520 --> 00:06:05.600
I really want to see

00:06:05.920 --> 00:06:08.600
if I can make it on my own.

00:06:08.800 --> 00:06:10.600
Isn't your dad mad at you?

00:06:10.680 --> 00:06:11.520
He is.

00:06:11.600 --> 00:06:12.960
He wants to disown me.

00:06:16.200 --> 00:06:17.800
I heard from Mom the other day

00:06:18.200 --> 00:06:20.400
that he always takes it
out on my elder sister.

00:06:21.000 --> 00:06:22.640
He yells so much she won't even visit.

00:06:23.080 --> 00:06:25.560
They always say I'm the only son.

00:06:25.720 --> 00:06:27.880
To me, my sister and I are the same.

00:06:28.680 --> 00:06:30.000
Come on, what year is it?

00:06:30.000 --> 00:06:31.760
Men and women are equal now.

00:06:31.920 --> 00:06:32.840
Old-fashioned.

00:06:33.360 --> 00:06:34.240
We're the same.

00:06:35.120 --> 00:06:36.360
I have an elder sister too.

00:06:36.920 --> 00:06:37.920
When my little brother was born,

00:06:37.920 --> 00:06:39.640
Dad put on an opera for the village.

00:06:41.280 --> 00:06:42.440
Did you really herd sheep?

00:06:44.280 --> 00:06:45.600
I had three sheep.

00:06:46.520 --> 00:06:47.680
We were close. They only

00:06:47.680 --> 00:06:48.640
listened to me.

00:06:53.800 --> 00:06:56.440
If my sister's in-laws hadn't said no,

00:06:57.240 --> 00:06:58.800
she'd be the one singing opera now,

00:06:59.400 --> 00:07:01.040
and I'd still herd sheep.

00:07:03.280 --> 00:07:04.320
Want to herd sheep?

00:07:04.320 --> 00:07:05.160
That's easy.

00:07:05.160 --> 00:07:06.120
It's a tiny thing.

00:07:06.640 --> 00:07:07.600
Let's get married,

00:07:07.600 --> 00:07:08.800
get a house with a yard,

00:07:08.880 --> 00:07:09.920
and raise three sheep.

00:07:09.920 --> 00:07:11.840
I shouldn't be nice to you, should I?

00:07:12.160 --> 00:07:14.160
You're talking absolute nonsense.

00:07:17.160 --> 00:07:19.400
Let's be serious, Qin'e.

00:07:20.080 --> 00:07:21.680
I think that fire was a good thing.

00:07:22.240 --> 00:07:24.680
Out with the old, in with the new.

00:07:27.360 --> 00:07:28.800
Qin'e,

00:07:29.400 --> 00:07:31.440
you're about to be famous!

00:07:32.040 --> 00:07:33.560
Super famous!

00:07:34.280 --> 00:07:36.080
Famous beyond Chang'an!

00:07:37.400 --> 00:07:39.320
Famous beyond China!

00:07:41.400 --> 00:07:43.160
Famous worldwide!

00:07:43.400 --> 00:07:45.160
Famous beyond Chang'an.

00:07:45.440 --> 00:07:47.200
Famous worldwide.

00:07:47.960 --> 00:07:49.640
Only someone shameless

00:07:49.640 --> 00:07:52.120
like Liu Hongbing could say that out loud.

00:07:52.840 --> 00:07:53.680
However,

00:07:53.800 --> 00:07:56.160
Yi Qin'e was still amused.

00:07:57.360 --> 00:07:58.840
She didn't know when it started,

00:07:59.720 --> 00:08:01.760
but Yi Qin'e began to feel that...

00:08:01.760 --> 00:08:02.680
(Qinchuan Qinqiang Opera Theater)

00:08:02.680 --> 00:08:05.120
Liu Hongbing wasn't so annoying.

00:08:05.120 --> 00:08:08.620
(You Xi Hu Starring
Yi Qin'e as Li Huiniang)

00:08:25.800 --> 00:08:27.330
- How's this?
- Good.

00:08:34.920 --> 00:08:35.760
So?

00:08:36.080 --> 00:08:37.000
It's beautiful.

00:10:07.440 --> 00:10:08.280
You can do it.

00:10:08.880 --> 00:10:10.120
So your first lesson

00:10:10.600 --> 00:10:11.880
is to have a goal.

00:10:12.000 --> 00:10:14.760
If you sing, you must be the lead.

00:10:16.320 --> 00:10:17.600
Bravo!

00:10:19.160 --> 00:10:20.000
Bravo!

00:10:20.960 --> 00:10:21.800
Bravo!

00:10:26.240 --> 00:10:28.560
You must learn to sing opera well.

00:10:29.040 --> 00:10:30.120
No matter how hard it is,

00:10:31.200 --> 00:10:32.360
you must keep going.

00:10:33.680 --> 00:10:35.120
Uncle's got your back.

00:10:35.680 --> 00:10:37.080
You just focus on singing.

00:10:37.600 --> 00:10:38.680
Together,

00:10:39.120 --> 00:10:40.200
we'll win this battle.

00:10:46.920 --> 00:10:47.960
Bravo!

00:11:10.760 --> 00:11:11.840
Bravo!

00:11:13.160 --> 00:11:14.000
Bravo!

00:11:22.640 --> 00:11:24.520
Bravo!

00:11:35.220 --> 00:11:38.740
(Qinchuan Qinqiang Opera Theater,
Ice Cream)

00:11:57.960 --> 00:11:58.800
Hu Sanyuan?

00:12:06.240 --> 00:12:07.080
What's wrong?

00:12:08.000 --> 00:12:09.560
Sitting here like a statue.

00:12:19.280 --> 00:12:20.120
What is it?

00:12:20.840 --> 00:12:22.240
Hadn't played the drums in a while.

00:12:22.680 --> 00:12:23.920
You got nervous?

00:12:25.600 --> 00:12:27.800
I wasn't keeping the beat for her.

00:12:29.000 --> 00:12:31.400
I was following her rhythm.

00:12:31.880 --> 00:12:33.360
Well, that's a good thing.

00:12:34.000 --> 00:12:34.960
A good thing...

00:12:35.560 --> 00:12:36.760
Of course, it is.

00:12:38.280 --> 00:12:40.320
Then why are you just sitting here?

00:12:44.600 --> 00:12:45.440
What?

00:12:46.360 --> 00:12:47.600
Feeling old?

00:12:47.680 --> 00:12:49.000
Surpassed by the kid?

00:12:49.240 --> 00:12:50.320
Feeling upset?

00:12:51.160 --> 00:12:52.400
Hard to explain.

00:12:57.120 --> 00:12:58.400
But for her path ahead,

00:12:59.880 --> 00:13:01.560
she really has to walk it alone.

00:13:08.960 --> 00:13:09.800
Let her.

00:13:14.160 --> 00:13:15.160
I can't help her anymore.

00:13:17.680 --> 00:13:18.600
I really can't.

00:13:22.820 --> 00:13:26.420
(You Xi Hu Starring
Yi Qin'e as Li Huiniang)

00:13:26.420 --> 00:13:30.860
(Qinchuan Qinqiang Opera Theater)

00:13:32.920 --> 00:13:33.760
Need tickets?

00:13:33.840 --> 00:13:35.320
Want tickets? Need tickets?

00:13:36.400 --> 00:13:37.520
You folks in line

00:13:38.080 --> 00:13:40.240
or just passing by,

00:13:40.600 --> 00:13:42.680
check out today's front-row tickets!

00:13:43.080 --> 00:13:44.600
Yes, yes. I've got them.

00:13:45.120 --> 00:13:46.600
Yours, Shuangyou's,

00:13:46.760 --> 00:13:47.720
and Xiaotong's.

00:13:47.760 --> 00:13:48.600
The tickets are set.

00:13:48.640 --> 00:13:50.000
Se... Secretary Wang.

00:13:50.120 --> 00:13:50.960
Right, right.

00:13:51.960 --> 00:13:54.120
Too much going on. I forgot.

00:13:54.120 --> 00:13:56.080
Got it. I'll send invites now.

00:13:56.080 --> 00:13:57.560
Right. Invites go out now.

00:13:57.560 --> 00:13:58.560
It's the grand finale.

00:13:58.560 --> 00:14:00.240
We need the leaders there to guide us.

00:14:01.720 --> 00:14:02.560
Yangping.

00:14:03.240 --> 00:14:05.600
Director Sun at Provincial
Radio Station: Two.

00:14:05.600 --> 00:14:06.560
Municipal Publicity...

00:14:06.640 --> 00:14:09.160
Sir, Provincial Department
of Culture called again.

00:14:09.560 --> 00:14:10.680
District Publicity Department.

00:14:10.800 --> 00:14:11.640
Director Sun.

00:14:11.930 --> 00:14:12.890
- Don't forget.
- Yeah.

00:14:12.890 --> 00:14:14.440
They are set! Sub-district...

00:14:14.440 --> 00:14:15.800
Remember, front row seats.

00:14:15.840 --> 00:14:17.160
There aren't enough front row seats!

00:14:17.680 --> 00:14:18.840
Just let them fight for it!

00:14:18.880 --> 00:14:20.320
Whoever gets the front row keeps it!

00:14:20.600 --> 00:14:22.920
Fire breathing comes in different types.

00:14:23.160 --> 00:14:25.320
For example, we have the single-puff one.

00:14:25.320 --> 00:14:26.280
Continuous one.

00:14:26.360 --> 00:14:27.440
Upward-facing.

00:14:27.440 --> 00:14:28.360
Dragon-like.

00:14:28.360 --> 00:14:29.640
Mushroom cloud.

00:14:30.160 --> 00:14:31.080
And so on.

00:14:31.240 --> 00:14:32.760
Each type of fire breathing

00:14:32.760 --> 00:14:35.400
has its own special meaning and purpose.

00:14:37.120 --> 00:14:38.120
Come on, brother.

00:14:38.200 --> 00:14:39.320
Still no sound?

00:14:39.320 --> 00:14:40.720
- I don't get it.
- Let me try.

00:14:40.720 --> 00:14:42.680
- Let me try!
- You don't know how, let me.

00:14:42.720 --> 00:14:44.000
Hurry up and find it.

00:14:45.320 --> 00:14:47.200
The county wants our village to get rich.

00:14:47.200 --> 00:14:48.240
That's a good thing.

00:14:49.640 --> 00:14:51.760
Our county's strength is the Boer goat.

00:14:52.640 --> 00:14:54.880
There's a good buying policy now.

00:14:55.120 --> 00:14:56.080
Sell the goats,

00:14:56.600 --> 00:14:57.840
and the money will come.

00:14:58.960 --> 00:14:59.800
Really?

00:14:59.960 --> 00:15:00.800
Yes, really.

00:15:01.080 --> 00:15:02.040
You should've said so earlier!

00:15:02.400 --> 00:15:04.360
The chickens and goats I raised before,

00:15:04.760 --> 00:15:06.280
I had them all as drinking snacks.

00:15:08.280 --> 00:15:10.160
Trying to talk to you foodies

00:15:10.760 --> 00:15:11.640
is just impossible.

00:15:18.200 --> 00:15:19.040
Qin'e!

00:15:21.960 --> 00:15:22.800
Qin'e!

00:15:23.920 --> 00:15:25.400
What's wrong? You okay?

00:15:27.800 --> 00:15:29.040
From the fire breathing?

00:15:30.600 --> 00:15:31.630
Who would've thought

00:15:31.630 --> 00:15:32.760
that practicing it

00:15:32.760 --> 00:15:34.040
would cause side effects?

00:15:34.240 --> 00:15:35.080
Feeling better?

00:15:36.400 --> 00:15:37.640
We agreed that after the premiere,

00:15:37.640 --> 00:15:38.840
you'd go back to work.

00:15:40.200 --> 00:15:41.440
I am at work now.

00:15:41.920 --> 00:15:43.400
I have a lunch break.

00:15:44.720 --> 00:15:46.160
I came to ask you.

00:15:47.360 --> 00:15:49.080
What do you want for dinner?

00:15:50.640 --> 00:15:51.840
Sour soup dumplings?

00:15:52.640 --> 00:15:53.560
I'll buy some.

00:16:01.400 --> 00:16:03.800
Liu, I was looking for you.

00:16:03.800 --> 00:16:04.640
What's up?

00:16:05.680 --> 00:16:08.080
The troupe is performing in Beijing.

00:16:08.440 --> 00:16:10.040
But I can't get train tickets.

00:16:10.320 --> 00:16:11.400
You're well-connected.

00:16:11.400 --> 00:16:12.800
Can you help us out?

00:16:13.360 --> 00:16:14.440
That's a tiny matter.

00:16:15.440 --> 00:16:17.200
I know a guy in the Ministry of Railways.

00:16:17.200 --> 00:16:18.680
We just played cards last week.

00:16:19.600 --> 00:16:21.600
How many hard seats and sleeper berths?

00:16:21.600 --> 00:16:22.520
Just tell me.

00:16:22.520 --> 00:16:23.640
Any tickets left?

00:16:23.640 --> 00:16:24.800
Excuse me, any tickets left?

00:16:24.800 --> 00:16:26.160
- Excuse me.
- Sold out.

00:16:26.190 --> 00:16:27.240
- Any tickets left?
- I'm...

00:16:27.240 --> 00:16:28.640
I'm Yi Qin'e's writer friend...

00:16:29.360 --> 00:16:30.200
(Sold out)
No more tickets.

00:16:30.960 --> 00:16:32.040
No, tickets are gone.

00:16:34.600 --> 00:16:35.440
No, thanks.

00:16:44.760 --> 00:16:45.600
No, thanks.

00:16:47.600 --> 00:16:48.680
- Go.
- No rush.

00:16:48.680 --> 00:16:49.960
Hold onto your tickets.

00:16:52.360 --> 00:16:53.200
Here.

00:16:55.960 --> 00:16:57.200
So many people are here.

00:16:57.200 --> 00:16:58.040
Wait.

00:17:02.680 --> 00:17:03.520
What day is it for?

00:17:04.240 --> 00:17:05.080
Today.

00:17:05.320 --> 00:17:06.320
You call yesterday today?

00:17:07.640 --> 00:17:08.480
Step aside!

00:17:10.600 --> 00:17:11.440
You got a problem?

00:17:11.960 --> 00:17:12.840
Fine, to the station.

00:17:14.680 --> 00:17:15.520
He ran off.

00:17:20.400 --> 00:17:21.240
Need a ticket?

00:17:21.840 --> 00:17:22.680
You have it?

00:17:26.160 --> 00:17:27.000
Don't push.

00:17:33.600 --> 00:17:35.120
Right now in Chang'an,

00:17:35.960 --> 00:17:37.920
except for trains to Shenzhen, Guangdong,

00:17:38.640 --> 00:17:40.880
(You Xi Hu)
You Xi Hu tickets are the rarest.

00:17:41.600 --> 00:17:42.440
Great, great.

00:17:43.120 --> 00:17:44.040
Old man,

00:17:44.280 --> 00:17:45.160
you have no tickets.

00:17:45.320 --> 00:17:46.280
How is it great?

00:17:46.520 --> 00:17:48.280
It proves that Qinqiang
opera is getting better.

00:17:48.840 --> 00:17:49.680
Will you buy it?

00:17:50.450 --> 00:17:51.700
- How much?
- One fifty.

00:17:52.680 --> 00:17:53.560
At the ticket office...

00:17:53.560 --> 00:17:55.440
You can't even get one, can you?

00:17:55.440 --> 00:17:56.380
Am I right?

00:17:56.400 --> 00:17:57.760
These are insider tickets.

00:17:58.600 --> 00:17:59.440
How are the seats?

00:18:00.000 --> 00:18:01.080
First-class?

00:18:01.360 --> 00:18:03.040
I guarantee you'll have

00:18:04.080 --> 00:18:05.280
the best seat.

00:18:13.000 --> 00:18:13.960
Where is it?

00:18:15.080 --> 00:18:15.920
What's the rush?

00:18:19.760 --> 00:18:20.920
Everyone, hold on a second.

00:18:20.920 --> 00:18:23.200
The leaders are here
to visit us. Welcome!

00:18:23.200 --> 00:18:24.400
Welcome!

00:18:24.400 --> 00:18:25.800
- Hello, everyone.
- Welcome, sir.

00:18:25.880 --> 00:18:26.720
You've worked hard.

00:18:27.800 --> 00:18:29.760
Wishing you a successful performance.

00:18:30.280 --> 00:18:32.520
In revitalizing Qinqiang opera,

00:18:32.520 --> 00:18:33.920
you've made a great start.

00:18:33.920 --> 00:18:36.360
We picked a great play this time.

00:18:36.600 --> 00:18:39.400
Especially the female lead, cast perfectly.

00:18:40.760 --> 00:18:41.600
Qin'e.

00:18:41.880 --> 00:18:42.880
Qin'e, come here.

00:18:45.080 --> 00:18:47.000
Sir, here she is.

00:18:47.040 --> 00:18:50.600
This is Yi Qin'e, playing Li Huiniang.

00:18:50.640 --> 00:18:51.960
She's the one you requested

00:18:51.960 --> 00:18:53.360
from Ningzhou back then.

00:18:53.560 --> 00:18:55.360
You truly have an eye for talent.

00:18:58.200 --> 00:19:00.080
A true talent. A true talent.

00:19:00.080 --> 00:19:01.120
Good. Good.

00:19:02.160 --> 00:19:04.520
Are there any other issues in your theater

00:19:04.520 --> 00:19:05.600
that need to be resolved?

00:19:05.720 --> 00:19:07.040
Issues?

00:19:08.120 --> 00:19:10.360
We can overcome any other issues,

00:19:10.720 --> 00:19:11.720
but there is just one...

00:19:11.720 --> 00:19:14.120
It's that Qin'e and the others are

00:19:14.120 --> 00:19:15.160
still living

00:19:15.160 --> 00:19:16.960
in felt shacks.

00:19:17.200 --> 00:19:18.560
Earlier, due to practicing

00:19:18.560 --> 00:19:19.800
the fire breathing,

00:19:19.800 --> 00:19:21.400
she almost caused a fire.

00:19:21.560 --> 00:19:24.120
Could you please find a way to resolve

00:19:24.120 --> 00:19:25.120
the accommodation issue?

00:19:26.720 --> 00:19:28.160
Are the actors' living

00:19:28.160 --> 00:19:29.800
conditions that harsh?

00:19:29.800 --> 00:19:30.680
Yes.

00:19:31.680 --> 00:19:33.760
It's the leadership's dereliction of duty.

00:19:34.560 --> 00:19:38.160
You can only work well if you live well.

00:19:39.360 --> 00:19:40.200
Troupe Leader,

00:19:40.600 --> 00:19:42.560
write a report and submit it to me.

00:19:42.600 --> 00:19:44.960
The province will sort it out for you.

00:19:45.120 --> 00:19:45.960
Thank you, sir!

00:19:46.320 --> 00:19:47.160
Thank you, sir!

00:19:48.080 --> 00:19:49.080
Thank you, sir!

00:19:50.400 --> 00:19:51.240
Thank you. Thank you.

00:19:51.320 --> 00:19:52.600
This way, please, sir.

00:19:52.600 --> 00:19:53.760
- Okay.
- Thank you, sir!

00:19:53.770 --> 00:19:55.060
- Okay.
- Good work, Troupe Leader.

00:19:56.640 --> 00:19:57.640
- Thank you, sir.
- Qin'e.

00:19:57.640 --> 00:19:59.000
You really helped us.

00:19:59.040 --> 00:20:00.680
If the housing gets approved,

00:20:00.720 --> 00:20:02.880
we all owe Qin'e our thanks, right?

00:20:02.880 --> 00:20:04.330
Right!

00:20:04.330 --> 00:20:05.430
Yes, absolutely.

00:20:08.640 --> 00:20:09.480
Listen.

00:20:09.880 --> 00:20:11.560
Is that my Laidi singing?

00:20:14.120 --> 00:20:14.960
Sounds like her.

00:20:15.680 --> 00:20:16.680
Oh, listen to you.

00:20:16.680 --> 00:20:18.120
Have you ever heard the kid sing?

00:20:18.920 --> 00:20:20.600
I watched your kid grow up.

00:20:20.760 --> 00:20:21.600
I can tell.

00:20:21.600 --> 00:20:22.680
How could I not tell?

00:20:24.560 --> 00:20:25.840
That's my Laidi.

00:20:26.720 --> 00:20:28.080
Singing so beautifully.

00:20:28.520 --> 00:20:30.000
It must be our Laidi!

00:20:30.000 --> 00:20:31.760
Exactly, she sings so well!

00:20:40.400 --> 00:20:42.520
Where are you taking me?

00:20:48.560 --> 00:20:50.520
♪Mister♪

00:20:52.860 --> 00:21:00.570
♪This flower is bright and pure♪

00:21:06.010 --> 00:21:12.320
♪Unlike the peach and plum blossoms♪

00:21:12.320 --> 00:21:20.400
♪Which wither and fall in the wind♪

00:21:26.260 --> 00:21:37.640
- ♪Plum blossoms are always there♪
- VIP spot! VIP experience!

00:21:37.640 --> 00:21:40.200
Don't touch anything.
Live wires everywhere.

00:21:46.540 --> 00:21:48.500
(Qinchuan Qinqiang Opera Theater)

00:21:48.520 --> 00:21:50.280
Bravo!

00:21:57.400 --> 00:21:59.120
You have such a big appetite!

00:21:59.120 --> 00:22:00.880
Here, have another bowl.

00:22:09.600 --> 00:22:10.920
Go easy on the chili.

00:22:12.600 --> 00:22:13.440
Sure.

00:22:13.760 --> 00:22:15.200
I'll make you a fresh bowl.

00:22:17.600 --> 00:22:19.120
I feel kinda sorry for you.

00:22:19.800 --> 00:22:20.800
You're tiny.

00:22:21.280 --> 00:22:22.640
How do you have so much energy?

00:22:23.800 --> 00:22:25.560
You count on this one meal all day.

00:22:26.400 --> 00:22:28.440
Eating so much at this hour.

00:22:28.680 --> 00:22:30.680
Only blacksmiths and
opera singers do this.

00:22:31.600 --> 00:22:33.280
Don't go to our theater tomorrow.

00:22:34.600 --> 00:22:35.840
Don't worry.

00:22:36.160 --> 00:22:37.160
The train tickets are sorted.

00:22:37.560 --> 00:22:38.400
Forty-six tickets.

00:22:38.440 --> 00:22:39.560
Forty-two hard seats.

00:22:39.560 --> 00:22:40.440
Four sleeper berths.

00:22:40.760 --> 00:22:41.680
I'll tell him to save

00:22:42.080 --> 00:22:43.240
a sleeper berth for you.

00:22:43.440 --> 00:22:45.040
Wouldn't sitting the whole way be torture?

00:22:45.960 --> 00:22:47.160
There are forty-five of us.

00:22:47.680 --> 00:22:48.640
Plus me.

00:22:49.320 --> 00:22:50.160
You are not going.

00:22:52.320 --> 00:22:53.640
What will you do if I don't go?

00:22:54.440 --> 00:22:55.920
I told you, I don't need you.

00:22:56.560 --> 00:22:57.600
You don't need me?

00:22:57.680 --> 00:22:59.000
What about the troupe?

00:23:00.160 --> 00:23:02.000
The hotel in Beijing?

00:23:02.280 --> 00:23:03.640
The round-trip bus?

00:23:03.640 --> 00:23:05.000
And the return tickets?

00:23:05.000 --> 00:23:07.000
Which part doesn't need me?

00:23:07.200 --> 00:23:08.520
Don't flatter yourself.

00:23:08.840 --> 00:23:10.680
The earth won't spin without you?

00:23:11.840 --> 00:23:14.240
Now you know my importance.

00:23:16.000 --> 00:23:17.360
Keep eating. I'll cook some more.

00:23:19.000 --> 00:23:19.840
Wait.

00:23:21.200 --> 00:23:22.560
I want a Bingfeng soda.

00:23:23.600 --> 00:23:24.440
Right now?

00:23:25.280 --> 00:23:26.120
Alright.

00:23:26.320 --> 00:23:28.280
It's a tiny matter. I'm on it.

00:23:55.840 --> 00:23:57.440
Here, your Bingfeng soda.

00:23:59.040 --> 00:23:59.960
You're done?

00:24:04.000 --> 00:24:04.840
Here.

00:24:06.600 --> 00:24:07.640
There are a few left.

00:24:08.200 --> 00:24:09.040
You finish them.

00:24:09.040 --> 00:24:10.160
Don't waste them.

00:24:10.600 --> 00:24:11.640
It's a tiny matter.

00:24:12.000 --> 00:24:13.680
Can't believe I got this lucky.

00:24:14.000 --> 00:24:15.680
I'll finish them off. Don't worry.

00:24:17.600 --> 00:24:18.840
You only left one anyway.

00:24:21.800 --> 00:24:22.760
Why skip the soup?

00:24:23.400 --> 00:24:24.680
Sour soup dumplings!

00:24:24.680 --> 00:24:26.280
The soup is the essence!

00:24:26.600 --> 00:24:27.440
Gotta drink it.

00:24:40.320 --> 00:24:41.240
So sour.

00:24:45.320 --> 00:24:46.160
Sir.

00:24:46.200 --> 00:24:47.400
You're the head of

00:24:47.400 --> 00:24:48.920
the Provincial Qinqiang Troupe,

00:24:49.120 --> 00:24:50.680
but you sit in a hard seat with us?

00:24:50.920 --> 00:24:52.600
You should have a sleeper berth.

00:24:52.600 --> 00:24:53.440
Right?

00:24:53.800 --> 00:24:55.920
Sleeper berths are for artists.

00:24:55.920 --> 00:24:57.280
Why would I need one?

00:24:57.560 --> 00:24:59.320
A hard seat is good enough.

00:25:00.000 --> 00:25:00.840
Look at you.

00:25:01.080 --> 00:25:03.440
Troupe Leader, why give
me a sleeper berth?

00:25:03.440 --> 00:25:05.430
I don't want it. You take it.

00:25:05.520 --> 00:25:06.680
Don't cause trouble.

00:25:06.680 --> 00:25:08.680
Just follow the rules on who gets to go.

00:25:09.080 --> 00:25:10.920
No, I just don't want special treatment.

00:25:10.920 --> 00:25:12.120
Give it to someone else.

00:25:12.600 --> 00:25:13.440
Who then?

00:25:13.680 --> 00:25:14.560
You decide.

00:25:14.560 --> 00:25:16.160
Troupe Leader, let me go instead.

00:25:16.440 --> 00:25:18.400
No way. Watch the suitcases.

00:25:19.360 --> 00:25:21.040
Troupe Leader, how about I go?

00:25:21.040 --> 00:25:22.160
My back isn't great.

00:25:22.280 --> 00:25:23.160
Go back now.

00:25:23.160 --> 00:25:24.760
Don't go to Beijing if your back is bad.

00:25:25.720 --> 00:25:27.280
Such a hassle.

00:25:28.760 --> 00:25:29.600
Move.

00:25:31.000 --> 00:25:31.840
Qin'e.

00:25:32.080 --> 00:25:33.240
Why don't you take it?

00:25:33.240 --> 00:25:35.920
You're our troupe's national treasure now.

00:25:36.520 --> 00:25:37.360
No need.

00:25:37.640 --> 00:25:39.080
I'm perfectly fine here with everyone.

00:25:39.800 --> 00:25:42.240
Now it's become a hot potato.

00:25:43.560 --> 00:25:44.400
Listen.

00:25:45.120 --> 00:25:46.440
As for these sleeper berth tickets,

00:25:46.440 --> 00:25:47.960
I'll keep them with me for now.

00:25:48.200 --> 00:25:49.560
Whoever gets tired

00:25:49.560 --> 00:25:50.920
can go there and take a nap.

00:25:50.920 --> 00:25:52.560
- Good. That works.
- Sure.

00:25:52.560 --> 00:25:53.600
Okay.

00:25:53.920 --> 00:25:54.760
- Here.
- Whose soda?

00:25:54.760 --> 00:25:56.400
- Mine.
- Why didn't Liu come?

00:25:57.600 --> 00:25:58.600
Why would he come?

00:25:59.920 --> 00:26:02.320
He handled the logistics really well

00:26:02.320 --> 00:26:03.400
for us.

00:26:09.640 --> 00:26:10.480
Qin'e,

00:26:11.520 --> 00:26:13.320
let me just say one more thing.

00:26:15.040 --> 00:26:16.760
For people like us,

00:26:17.520 --> 00:26:18.720
the most important thing

00:26:18.800 --> 00:26:21.200
is to have a stable family,

00:26:21.680 --> 00:26:23.280
and someone who supports you.

00:26:24.040 --> 00:26:26.960
These two things are better than anything.

00:26:27.640 --> 00:26:29.680
Now I just want to sing the opera well

00:26:30.720 --> 00:26:31.920
without distractions.

00:26:33.200 --> 00:26:34.720
I said too much. I did.

00:26:35.600 --> 00:26:36.680
Go on.

00:26:42.240 --> 00:26:44.290
Our Qinqiang opera going to Beijing

00:26:44.290 --> 00:26:45.640
is a huge deal, isn't it?

00:26:46.840 --> 00:26:47.680
Yes.

00:26:48.520 --> 00:26:50.760
We're carrying our predecessors' legacy.

00:26:51.440 --> 00:26:52.800
Shouldn't we do our best?

00:26:53.040 --> 00:26:54.100
- We must.
- Exactly.

00:26:55.640 --> 00:27:04.640
♪So bitter♪

00:27:32.840 --> 00:27:53.440
♪Resentment rises♪

00:27:57.640 --> 00:28:03.000
♪Three thousand feet high♪

00:28:05.640 --> 00:28:18.560
♪Three thousand feet high♪

00:29:05.680 --> 00:29:26.440
♪Wronged♪

00:29:27.560 --> 00:29:44.640
♪Souls are filled with rage♪

00:29:57.240 --> 00:29:58.870
The audience in the capital...

00:30:00.560 --> 00:30:02.360
can't understand our Qinqiang opera?

00:30:04.560 --> 00:30:05.400
Impossible.

00:30:05.800 --> 00:30:07.560
Art is universal.

00:30:08.920 --> 00:30:10.080
Take Italian opera,

00:30:10.440 --> 00:30:12.280
it's sung all over the world.

00:30:14.720 --> 00:30:15.920
You're absolutely right.

00:30:19.920 --> 00:30:21.520
The audience today

00:30:21.520 --> 00:30:23.160
is full of professionals.

00:30:23.720 --> 00:30:25.880
They're all here to judge.

00:30:27.620 --> 00:30:30.600
Qin'e's part isn't easy to sing.

00:30:46.780 --> 00:30:52.420
(Diaojia Village)

00:32:22.400 --> 00:32:29.400
Bravo!

00:32:29.400 --> 00:32:35.480
Bravo!

00:32:39.560 --> 00:32:41.280
That was amazing!

00:32:41.720 --> 00:32:42.600
I'm so thrilled!

00:32:42.600 --> 00:32:44.400
Great! Absolutely amazing!

00:32:44.400 --> 00:32:46.640
You handled the logistics so well!

00:32:47.080 --> 00:32:48.640
Hongbing, when did you arrive?

00:32:49.000 --> 00:32:51.000
I told you, planes are super fast.

00:32:51.680 --> 00:32:53.440
From Yuxiang Gate to Tian'anmen,

00:32:53.600 --> 00:32:54.640
it only took three hours.

00:32:56.680 --> 00:32:59.080
A sandalwood fan from the plane. Take it.

00:33:00.520 --> 00:33:02.160
Thank you, Hongbing.

00:33:02.160 --> 00:33:03.520
Great job on the show. Well done.

00:33:04.440 --> 00:33:05.280
Qin'e.

00:33:06.360 --> 00:33:07.580
- Why are you here?
- A gift?

00:33:07.600 --> 00:33:08.760
It was spectacular!

00:33:08.840 --> 00:33:09.680
Hungry?

00:33:10.000 --> 00:33:11.240
I brought some Guokui.

00:33:11.320 --> 00:33:12.920
Hurry, have a bite.

00:33:12.920 --> 00:33:13.760
I can't eat.

00:33:15.000 --> 00:33:15.840
Qin'e.

00:33:20.280 --> 00:33:21.120
Everyone.

00:33:21.840 --> 00:33:24.240
The Performance Selection Team came tonight,

00:33:24.800 --> 00:33:26.360
and they chose us

00:33:26.360 --> 00:33:29.320
for the excerpts, Gui Yuan and Sha Sheng.

00:33:29.320 --> 00:33:31.000
This Friday night,

00:33:31.200 --> 00:33:33.000
we'll put on a showcase for them.

00:33:33.720 --> 00:33:35.120
If we do well, we'll get to

00:33:35.320 --> 00:33:37.520
join the National
Traditional Opera Festival.

00:33:37.880 --> 00:33:39.200
It is the country's

00:33:39.320 --> 00:33:40.760
highest-level performance.

00:33:42.600 --> 00:33:43.440
Everyone.

00:33:47.320 --> 00:33:48.560
During the Qianlong Era,

00:33:49.880 --> 00:33:50.880
Wei Changsheng

00:33:55.320 --> 00:33:58.360
brought Qinqiang opera to Beijing.

00:33:59.840 --> 00:34:01.240
It's been over 200 years.

00:34:05.080 --> 00:34:06.400
Over 200 years.

00:34:09.520 --> 00:34:11.080
The revival of Qinqiang opera

00:34:12.400 --> 00:34:13.600
depends on you guys!

00:34:14.640 --> 00:34:18.000
Yeah! Yeah!

00:34:18.000 --> 00:34:19.600
- Awesome!
- Yeah!

00:34:19.800 --> 00:34:21.440
We won't let you down!

00:34:21.440 --> 00:34:23.600
We'll revive Qinqiang opera!

00:34:30.920 --> 00:34:32.160
My... My stomach hurts!

00:34:32.160 --> 00:34:33.520
- Hurry!
- What's wrong?

00:34:33.760 --> 00:34:34.880
Upset stomach!

00:34:54.600 --> 00:34:55.440
Qin'e?

00:34:56.600 --> 00:34:57.440
Qin'e!

00:34:58.120 --> 00:35:00.240
- Look!
- Why didn't you knock again?

00:35:01.120 --> 00:35:02.160
Don't be mad.

00:35:02.600 --> 00:35:03.760
I'll be careful.

00:35:03.760 --> 00:35:05.680
The wardrobe and makeup crew live here.

00:35:06.400 --> 00:35:08.720
I saw them still busy in the makeup room.

00:35:08.720 --> 00:35:09.560
Look.

00:35:10.040 --> 00:35:11.520
I just went to Wangfujing.

00:35:11.520 --> 00:35:13.400
I got you some Qingfeng Baozi.

00:35:13.400 --> 00:35:15.120
And these hot Wontons.

00:35:15.120 --> 00:35:17.040
Eat something warm before you sleep.

00:35:17.160 --> 00:35:18.000
No appetite.

00:35:19.000 --> 00:35:19.880
I figured.

00:35:20.720 --> 00:35:21.640
Not used to the food?

00:35:21.880 --> 00:35:22.720
Look.

00:35:22.920 --> 00:35:25.600
We have Jinggao from Chang'an.

00:35:25.600 --> 00:35:27.040
I have no appetite.

00:35:29.200 --> 00:35:30.360
I don't blame your anger.

00:35:31.160 --> 00:35:32.520
The other day,

00:35:32.880 --> 00:35:34.200
I don't know what I ate,

00:35:34.200 --> 00:35:35.440
but I suddenly got a

00:35:35.440 --> 00:35:36.320
bad stomachache.

00:35:36.320 --> 00:35:38.040
I couldn't even get out of bed.

00:35:38.400 --> 00:35:39.760
That's why I missed the train

00:35:40.280 --> 00:35:41.320
and got here late.

00:35:41.600 --> 00:35:43.040
I suspect that

00:35:43.400 --> 00:35:45.160
it was the sour soup dumplings.

00:35:45.760 --> 00:35:47.600
I feared your stomach was upset.

00:35:47.600 --> 00:35:49.320
So I rushed all the way to Beijing

00:35:49.320 --> 00:35:50.560
to take care of you.

00:35:50.720 --> 00:35:52.760
Are you feeling better now?

00:35:53.120 --> 00:35:54.880
I'm fine. Pretty much recovered.

00:35:57.920 --> 00:35:58.760
What?

00:35:59.600 --> 00:36:01.720
You worried about me?

00:36:02.600 --> 00:36:05.000
Since you're better, go back and rest.

00:36:05.240 --> 00:36:07.360
- No more running around.
- Okay.

00:36:07.360 --> 00:36:09.760
Have some warm soup before bed.

00:36:09.760 --> 00:36:12.760
- Rest up.
- Thanks for caring, milady.

00:36:16.880 --> 00:36:19.840
Zhang Yiyuan tea is 15 yuan a jin.

00:36:21.360 --> 00:36:22.360
Eighteen.

00:36:22.960 --> 00:36:24.090
So that's nine each.

00:36:24.090 --> 00:36:26.680
- Nine each.
- One hundred twenty-five.

00:36:27.760 --> 00:36:29.080
Can you even do the math?

00:36:29.080 --> 00:36:29.960
It's 135.

00:36:30.120 --> 00:36:31.600
I took six. Take a look.

00:36:31.920 --> 00:36:33.280
Silly me.

00:36:35.440 --> 00:36:36.600
Twenty.

00:36:36.600 --> 00:36:37.440
Check it.

00:36:38.360 --> 00:36:39.960
Five each. One hundred.

00:36:39.960 --> 00:36:41.000
Right, one hundred.

00:36:41.160 --> 00:36:43.320
Eight bottles of Liubiju.

00:36:43.800 --> 00:36:44.760
I told you.

00:36:44.800 --> 00:36:46.560
Sweet pickled radish only, no cucumbers.

00:36:46.560 --> 00:36:47.800
I can't split this with you.

00:36:47.800 --> 00:36:49.680
Why didn't you say so when we bought it?

00:36:50.240 --> 00:36:51.920
I did. You just didn't hear me.

00:37:01.280 --> 00:37:03.040
Actors, listen to me.

00:37:03.080 --> 00:37:04.320
Play full, sing hungry.

00:37:04.560 --> 00:37:05.640
However good Zhajiangmian is,

00:37:05.640 --> 00:37:06.840
don't eat too much.

00:37:06.840 --> 00:37:07.840
Stay in shape.

00:37:07.840 --> 00:37:09.360
- Okay, Director.
- Okay.

00:37:09.840 --> 00:37:11.520
You're an actor, why eat garlic?

00:37:11.520 --> 00:37:13.310
- You'll reek on stage.
- I'm not kissing.

00:37:13.360 --> 00:37:14.400
You don't have any

00:37:14.400 --> 00:37:15.960
professional ethics as an actor.

00:37:16.840 --> 00:37:17.680
Here.

00:37:18.560 --> 00:37:19.580
What is it?

00:37:19.600 --> 00:37:21.600
Hongbing brought you this pear soup.

00:37:21.600 --> 00:37:23.040
He knows you can't eat,

00:37:23.040 --> 00:37:24.520
but you must soothe your throat.

00:37:24.520 --> 00:37:25.360
Where is he?

00:37:25.600 --> 00:37:26.920
He left after giving it to me.

00:37:28.840 --> 00:37:30.800
The Saozi and Zhajiang are great today.

00:37:41.160 --> 00:37:43.080
(Canteen)
Everyone, wear your ID badges.

00:37:43.800 --> 00:37:44.640
Remember,

00:37:44.760 --> 00:37:46.360
except when you're performing on stage,

00:37:46.360 --> 00:37:47.560
no one at any time

00:37:47.560 --> 00:37:48.960
can take off this pass.

00:37:48.960 --> 00:37:50.600
- Understood?
- Got it.

00:37:50.720 --> 00:37:51.960
- Board the bus.
- Qin'e.

00:37:52.600 --> 00:37:54.040
Just perform as you normally do.

00:37:54.520 --> 00:37:55.360
No problem.

00:37:55.360 --> 00:37:56.320
Just perform as usual.

00:37:57.520 --> 00:37:58.920
Hurry up, go on.

00:38:23.140 --> 00:38:29.780
(Canteen)

00:38:34.280 --> 00:38:35.920
Sir, want some water?

00:38:50.320 --> 00:38:51.520
Here they come!

00:38:51.680 --> 00:38:52.520
They're here!

00:38:53.360 --> 00:38:54.320
What's the matter?

00:38:55.560 --> 00:38:57.360
They didn't even arrange a bus?

00:38:57.680 --> 00:38:58.680
They failed?

00:39:08.000 --> 00:39:08.840
How was it?

00:39:23.400 --> 00:39:24.240
Troupe Leader...

00:39:25.520 --> 00:39:26.400
Sorry.

00:39:28.520 --> 00:39:29.680
Today's performance...

00:39:34.400 --> 00:39:36.400
was a huge success!

00:39:39.120 --> 00:39:41.120
You scared me!

00:39:48.600 --> 00:39:49.440
Great!

00:39:50.800 --> 00:39:51.640
Qin'e!

00:39:52.360 --> 00:39:53.200
Qin'e!

00:39:53.360 --> 00:39:54.200
We did it!

00:39:54.520 --> 00:39:55.360
Qin'e!

00:39:56.320 --> 00:39:57.160
Qin'e!

00:39:58.720 --> 00:39:59.560
Alright, alright.

00:40:00.520 --> 00:40:01.760
Our Qinqiang opera succeeded!

00:40:01.760 --> 00:40:02.640
Listen...

00:40:04.240 --> 00:40:05.360
Let go!

00:40:05.360 --> 00:40:06.440
We must drink!

00:40:06.440 --> 00:40:07.280
Sure!

00:40:08.760 --> 00:40:09.600
Qin'e!

00:40:10.520 --> 00:40:11.360
Qin'e!

00:40:12.240 --> 00:40:13.080
Don't hug me!

00:40:22.240 --> 00:40:23.080
Our pot isn't here yet.

00:40:23.440 --> 00:40:25.200
The pot is here! Come on.

00:40:25.320 --> 00:40:26.760
Make way. Here.

00:40:28.760 --> 00:40:30.920
Eat and drink up, everyone!

00:40:31.000 --> 00:40:33.200
Plenty of meat and booze!

00:40:37.040 --> 00:40:38.560
Hongbing is so generous!

00:40:39.160 --> 00:40:40.760
We've got liquor and beer!

00:40:40.760 --> 00:40:42.400
Don't just talk. Drink up!

00:40:42.400 --> 00:40:44.440
Drink up! Drink up!

00:40:44.560 --> 00:40:45.400
Two beers.

00:40:45.400 --> 00:40:47.080
Troupe Leader, drink up!

00:40:47.410 --> 00:40:48.870
- Here you go.
- Come on.

00:40:50.680 --> 00:40:52.320
We have meat and drinks!

00:40:53.400 --> 00:40:54.280
Pour it up.

00:40:54.280 --> 00:40:55.720
Go easy, don't drink too much.

00:40:56.200 --> 00:40:58.560
Troupe Leader, let me update you on today.

00:40:58.800 --> 00:41:00.400
Today, Comrade Qin'e

00:41:00.400 --> 00:41:02.400
really outdid herself!

00:41:02.720 --> 00:41:04.680
Every frown, smile and move

00:41:04.680 --> 00:41:06.840
was absolutely perfect.

00:41:07.000 --> 00:41:09.440
If ten guys from the Business Department

00:41:09.440 --> 00:41:11.080
stared with wide eyes,

00:41:11.080 --> 00:41:13.360
they wouldn't find a single flaw.

00:41:13.560 --> 00:41:14.520
- Right?
- Exactly!

00:41:14.520 --> 00:41:15.740
Well said, that's right!

00:41:15.740 --> 00:41:17.760
Guess how we handled the fire breathing?

00:41:17.760 --> 00:41:18.600
How?

00:41:19.360 --> 00:41:20.240
Wait, wait!

00:41:20.560 --> 00:41:21.680
Don't say a word.

00:41:22.080 --> 00:41:23.280
Just because of it,

00:41:23.280 --> 00:41:24.920
the Troupe Leader owes us a drink!

00:41:25.000 --> 00:41:26.000
No problem!

00:41:26.180 --> 00:41:28.600
- I still have to drink my share.
- Come on.

00:41:28.600 --> 00:41:29.650
- Drink up.
- Okay.

00:41:29.650 --> 00:41:30.730
Alright, bro.

00:41:31.240 --> 00:41:32.080
Troupe Leader.

00:41:32.920 --> 00:41:34.840
I need to discuss something with you.

00:41:34.840 --> 00:41:35.680
Go ahead.

00:41:37.000 --> 00:41:39.280
I want a few days off back in Chang'an.

00:41:39.280 --> 00:41:40.800
No problem. That's fine.

00:41:41.960 --> 00:41:43.320
But after we get back,

00:41:43.360 --> 00:41:46.360
the province will surely
commend us, right?

00:41:46.360 --> 00:41:47.520
By popular demand,

00:41:47.520 --> 00:41:49.280
You Xi Hu will definitely have

00:41:49.280 --> 00:41:50.160
extra shows.

00:41:50.160 --> 00:41:52.640
After the extra shows, rest all you want.

00:41:52.640 --> 00:41:54.160
Take as much time off

00:41:54.160 --> 00:41:55.400
as you need.

00:41:55.400 --> 00:41:56.240
Okay.

00:41:56.320 --> 00:41:57.920
- Cheers.
- You guys drink up.

00:42:00.520 --> 00:42:01.360
Troupe Leader.

00:42:01.640 --> 00:42:02.960
How's your chat going?

00:42:03.160 --> 00:42:05.320
I'd like to borrow Comrade Qin'e for a bit.

00:42:05.320 --> 00:42:06.840
Go ahead. Go ahead.

00:42:10.920 --> 00:42:11.760
Alright!

00:42:12.080 --> 00:42:14.000
Everyone, please quiet down.

00:42:14.320 --> 00:42:17.640
First, I want to congratulate everyone here

00:42:18.000 --> 00:42:22.560
on the huge success of the Beijing show.

00:42:22.560 --> 00:42:23.970
Great!

00:42:24.130 --> 00:42:25.080
Great!

00:42:25.080 --> 00:42:26.740
- Let's drink!
- Drink!

00:42:26.760 --> 00:42:27.600
Drink!

00:42:28.240 --> 00:42:29.240
- Hongbing!
- Cheers!

00:42:29.240 --> 00:42:30.080
Cheers!

00:42:30.080 --> 00:42:30.960
Good job.

00:42:30.990 --> 00:42:32.640
- Thank you, sir.
- Drink up!

00:42:34.520 --> 00:42:35.640
For this second cup,

00:42:37.320 --> 00:42:39.200
I'd like to toast Comrade Yi Qin'e.

00:42:42.960 --> 00:42:43.920
To be honest,

00:42:44.440 --> 00:42:46.600
my life before meeting Yi Qin'e

00:42:46.640 --> 00:42:48.640
was completely aimless.

00:42:49.080 --> 00:42:50.720
I never really saw the point of life.

00:42:51.600 --> 00:42:53.040
In the blink of an eye,

00:42:53.240 --> 00:42:54.920
all those years just passed by.

00:42:56.680 --> 00:42:57.520
But...

00:42:59.320 --> 00:43:00.320
It's different now.

00:43:01.000 --> 00:43:02.000
Even eating liangpi

00:43:03.080 --> 00:43:03.920
makes me happy.

00:43:05.020 --> 00:43:06.940
=The Lead=
(Preview)

00:43:09.120 --> 00:43:10.360
Comrade Yi Qin'e

00:43:10.360 --> 00:43:13.180
has been blessed with
every gift for the opera.

00:43:13.180 --> 00:43:16.080
During shows, you barely
have time to eat or drink.

00:43:16.080 --> 00:43:18.000
Luckily, Hongbing's always there for you.

00:43:18.000 --> 00:43:19.960
Bro, are you proposing or what?

00:43:20.000 --> 00:43:22.440
Get down on one knee! One knee!

00:43:22.440 --> 00:43:24.320
I told you, we aren't suited for each other!

00:43:24.550 --> 00:43:26.720
This is what's hottest right now!

00:43:26.720 --> 00:43:27.880
Rock 'n' roll!

00:43:28.680 --> 00:43:30.920
Qinqiang opera has to change.

00:43:31.400 --> 00:43:32.560
But how should it change?

00:43:37.000 --> 00:43:41.620
♪When I woke up and turned back♪

00:43:43.090 --> 00:43:47.930
♪I wasn't sure where to go♪

00:43:49.370 --> 00:43:53.560
♪We met and brushed past♪

00:43:55.120 --> 00:44:02.420
♪Your shadow drifted out of sight♪

00:44:16.790 --> 00:44:20.540
♪The stove fire blazed in my dream♪

00:44:22.140 --> 00:44:27.710
♪Lit up the tracks of pearly tears♪

00:44:28.830 --> 00:44:32.890
♪In my dream, water sleeves flew♪

00:44:34.020 --> 00:44:39.610
♪Hiding a lifetime of love♪

00:44:40.770 --> 00:44:44.970
♪The Qinling Mountains
crossed the stage♪

00:44:46.010 --> 00:44:51.640
♪Spring water brewed strong wine♪

00:44:52.810 --> 00:44:57.500
♪Sheep moved through the valley♪

00:44:58.180 --> 00:45:03.350
♪It felt like a promise
from another life♪

00:45:04.020 --> 00:45:09.050
♪When I woke up and turned back♪

00:45:10.080 --> 00:45:15.510
♪I wasn't sure where to go♪

00:45:15.890 --> 00:45:21.170
♪If I chose again, I'd still roam♪

00:45:22.120 --> 00:45:27.930
♪All over this sunlit plateau♪

00:45:27.930 --> 00:45:33.350
♪The dream ends; the curtain falls♪

00:45:33.900 --> 00:45:39.410
♪Moonlight washes off this stage makeup♪

00:45:39.960 --> 00:45:44.920
♪The one in the mirror wears gray hair♪

00:45:45.940 --> 00:45:51.220
♪Already sang all my joy and sorrow♪

00:45:52.020 --> 00:46:01.050
♪Already shouted across Qinchuan Plain♪